                    </div>
                    <div class="text-left">
                        <h6 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-700 dark:text-white">KnowledgeOwl <span class="text-primary dark:text-sky-300">with sass</span></h6>
                        <p class="mt-2 text-gray-500">Considering or already using KnowledgeOwl? Work with a KO expert.</p>
                    </div>
                </div>
